{"tid":2147358,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁國勇：6月放寬措施是大錯","createTime":"2020-08-09T07:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T07:45:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7605821fc520ce145eea7e4694768bc049d88851","tid":2147358,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:45:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200809/F3L5WKIOGOK7EVKEE7INGZ4F54/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200809%2FF3L5WKIOGOK7EVKEE7INGZ4F54%2F&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminIXq8Qv2IeoILbHjSh09rgU%3D&h=f0b01dc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200809%2FF3L5WKIOGOK7EVKEE7INGZ4F54%2F&h=91f90d7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200809/F3L5WKIOGOK7EVKEE7INGZ4F54/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇：6月放寬措施是大錯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hrVxTwnhqYQrLs0sPk3-8dJTk8o=/640x507/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KUJ3MRLOQAKIWCIWREJJ4MSIUE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhrVxTwnhqYQrLs0sPk3-8dJTk8o%3D%2F640x507%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKUJ3MRLOQAKIWCIWREJJ4MSIUE.jpg&h=bafe3176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n袁國勇昨表示現階段難以評估全民檢測計劃成效。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】第三波疫潮至今已有近3,000人確診，奪去了40名香港人生命，元凶之一是特首林鄭月娥豁免海員等32類入境入士檢疫。<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"large\">袁國勇指，第三波疫潮主要是本地個案，相信源頭是港府的豁免檢測安排，加上當局6月放寬防疫措施，市民鬆懈，街上人頭湧湧，約一成人沒戴口罩，明顯是很大錯誤。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n袁國勇期望政府吸取教訓，<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"large\">「第一樣嘢，搞好關口，真係防疫要做足，真係夠晒嚴，以致你唔會咁多漏網之魚」</span></span>。即使有漏網之魚，仍應採取方法控制高危地點，「譬如我哋𠵱家講明街市同埋超市，應該做嘅好多都冇做到，咁你落實唔到嘅話，你一放鬆一定出事。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指批鬥對社會毫無好處<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：化驗師與外判關係複雜<br />\n<br />\n他續稱，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"large\">他相信，港人要捱多9至12個月，本港才可引入疫苗，屆時才有望重返正常生活。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n袁國勇早前接受BBC訪問時提及。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他的港大工作部門最近有三名同事會離職，袁國勇指出，在香港大學工作超過35年，轄下受訓醫生眾多，部份人到史丹福大學、哈佛大學等著名海外學府任教，對他來說是一種榮譽，也有些人選擇移民，「係開心事」，。。。。。。。。。。。。。」"}]}